				<td colspan="2"><span>The song hits then drops is <i>not</i> a bug. It's simply a lag issue. Client side you get the song off in time, but the server doesn't know it has gone off for a relatively long period of time. So you see the song refreshed, because the client calculated that it was refreshed, but the server corrects the client and you lose the buff that you never really had. </span></td>
